item.title: About
item.description: OhmJet is community based electric vehicle charging ecosystem. The company was established in 2024 year in Western Balkans. Our goal is to make EV charging more affordable and scalable. The company was founded by programmers, engineers, fintech, and marketing professionals who could not imagine life without electric vehicles. So we have combined financial technology and electronic engineering under the one hood. What does OhmJet offer to market? Our company does not resell the equipment.

item.title: How it works
item.description: Our mission is a boost EV’s Residential Charging market. Instead of developing a massive fast charging stations network, we are working on our own community-based EV charging ecosystem. For Drivers We offer a simple and clear EV charging experience. Use our host offers listing to find the best spot for your final destination. Book a table, apartment, or parking slot, and be sure that your car will be charged. Download Mobile App Top-up your OhmJet balance Plug your car to charging station Read QR and calculate charge times Walk, Eat, Sleep and Go You will be able to use a contactless experience.
